### Create a ride (string start_location)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/rides
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Madrid Evening Ride",
  "date_time": "2025-09-20T18:00:00",
  "pace": "Easy",
  "distance_km": 45,
  "start_location": "Retiro Park, Madrid",
  "coffee_shop_id": 1
}

